osts":[{"id":37223,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/25\/resurrected-deen-death\/","url_meta":{"origin":9916,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Resurrection: Each resurrected with their religion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 25, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEvery servant in his grave will be resurrected upon the way he died, the believer upon his faith and the hypocrite upon his hypocrisy.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 14722 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24306,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/01\/27\/sincerity-muslims-hellfire-forever\/","url_meta":{"origin":9916,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ikhlaas: Sincere Muslims do not stay in Hellfire forever","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 27, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"'Itban ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came to me one morning and a man said, \u201cWhere is Malik ibn al-Dukhshun?\u201d Another man among us said, \u201cThat one is a hypocrite! He does not love Allah and His Messenger!\u201d The Prophet said to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11580,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/22\/dua-salat-ala-al-nabi-most\/","url_meta":{"origin":9916,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salawat: Nearest to Prophet blessed him most","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe closest of people to me on the Day of Resurrection are those who sent the most blessings upon me.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 484 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37260,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/27\/dua-for-shafaa\/","url_meta":{"origin":9916,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication to guarantee the Prophet\u2019s intercession","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ruwayfah ibn Thabit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever sends blessings upon Muhammad by saying, \u2018O Allah, grant him the seat near You on the Day of Resurrection,\u2019 then my intercession is ensured for him.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 16991 Grade: Hasan (fair) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38605,"url":